  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2>Admin Dashboard</h2>
          <p>Welcome to your admin dashboard. From here, you can manage users, courses, departments, and view reports.</p>

          <div class="list-group">
            <a href="/viewUsers" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
